<P>ACTS AND LAWS, Passed by the Great and General Court or Assembly of Their Majesties Province of the Massachusetts-Bay, in NEW-ENGLAND. Convened and Held at <HI>Boston,</HI> the Eight Day of <HI>November.</HI> 1693.</P>
<P>Anno Regni Guilielmi, et Mariae, Regis et Reginae, Angliae, Scotiae, Franciae, et Hiberniae, Quinto.</P>
<P>BOSTON. Printed by <HI>Bartholomew Green,</HI> and Sold by <HI>Samuel Phillips.</HI> 1693.</P>
</DIV1>
